reviewText: "This (Season 5: Voyage Three) of the anime series (One Piece), was a great & enjoyable show to watch.""I really enjoyed the suggestive sections; Such as the audio language section, and the translation subtitles language section as well."
summary: This (One Piece) anime series has great story line & characters are also great.
Title: One Piece: Season 5, Voyage Three

reviewText: The Enies Lobby arc is finally in full swing after the flashback extravaganza that was voyage two. This set features several intense fights and quite a few funny moments. If you are a One Piece fan you must watch this as Enies Lobby is one of the best arcs this series has to offer!
summary: Enies Lobby is really heating up!
Title: One Piece: Season 5, Voyage Three

reviewText: This is all out fighting package the straw hats vs cp9 a lot of fights get concluded but not all of them. Overall this is a great box set and it is awesome to watch. P.S. there are only two filler episodes but they are good ones.
Title: One Piece: Season 5, Voyage Three

reviewText: this story is really getting good right now and it just keeps getting better with more intense fights intense story too
Title: One Piece: Season 5, Voyage Three

reviewText: It's One Piece, who can say it is anything but spectacular. I do have to say that I can't recall how many are on this disk, but there are quite a few fillers that may drive you a bit nuts. Personally I skipped them since they had nothing to do with the main storyline. But at least they weren't as bad as some other Anime's (such as the 6 seasons worth of fillers in Naruto! UGH!)...Either way I am positive you will love this.
Title: One Piece: Season 5, Voyage Three
